I went and saw him today...

 I know now why I feel so far from you. I can't tell you what I think. And I hate it. I am so open minded and outspoken, but with you... I would rather just shut you out and not try. Why can't I just tell you when you, you upset me... Or hurt my feelings. I guess I think you will think I am an idiot. It makes me think so differently about you. Or Maybe its the confusion that I purposely brought back into my life tonight?! Why Am I so damn stubborn?

 

For some reason I feel better.

I hate everyone and everything right now. I am so full of confusion and anger. I take things to heart that I know I shouldn't then, I sit there and look at them and feel like I am worthless. I make it worse than it should be... Then want pity. I hate myself, I hate my life. I automatically twist ppls words and thoughts into something that I KNOW will upset, me jsut to be upset. I walked around school today all day, pissed at the world. I Couldn't hide my disgust for ppl. I have no friends I feel, the ppl that come into my life I push away. I have you to thank you fucking asshole. You made me like this, I can't trust anyone!!! I don't trust myself. I hate you for that, but love you cuz I have too. I wish you would just go away and never talk to me again. But U dont', You always come back and throw me off. I AM LOST!!!!!!! This is hopeless. Trying to explain yourslef is never going to help, and especially when its to ppl that don't even KNOW you. I feel trapped in a life i can't escape. I JUST WANT OUT...

I feel like going out and having the time of my life...

I got a 24 on my ACT. That would be great if... (ya there is always something huh?) I had a grade point average of 3.5 or higher. Well I don't.

I don't work tonight. I am excited. TOmorrow, however, I have to open and close?! SOund weird? It is.

I decided to let go of all that drama about the senior trip. It doesn't really matter. If someone or a group of ppl doesn't like me, you know what? Thats fine. They probably aren't worth my time anyway. I am ok.

Well I am sitting here waiting for my friend to call me and make plans. But I guess I will check you cats later.

HOLLA BITCHES

Ok friday I had begun to feel alot better. My fever went down, I didn't have a headache... YOu know I was BETTER! Well Lastnight at work or really that whole day (saturday) I felt like crap, my head had begun to hurt again and my chest... wow, it felt like I couldn't breath! I have to take shallow little breaths... or else I think I will cough up a lung. 

So even though I felt like crap I worked lastnight. I came home to find my temperature was back up and at 101 Degrees. YAY, I'm friggin sick agian (sarcasm).

I can say however that I am glad. I have so far lost 8 pounds from being sick. Muahahaha. That is s00o0o sad. I had bought a 3 pair of jeans, one pair I picked up were not the right size (too small)... Hey now they fit. Thats great!

Oh Well I gotta go get my check and go to THE AFTER HOURS CLINIC... So Ya, I may not be at school again kids. PLEASE GET ALL OF MY ASSIGNMENTS.

:Coughs: I <3 you guys.

Your Love Number is
6

Who you fall in love with is all about who you trust. Loyalty is important to you, and you want the most faithful of lovers. In return, you never let your heart or eyes wander. Open and honest, your relationships tend to be free of secrets.
What Is Your Love Number?

I just got a fone call from someone that hasn't spoken to me since she last broke up with her boyfriend.

Ya, well of course they are having "problems". Their whole relationship is a problem. He doesn't even allow her to hang out with her friends.

When I was tlaking to her on the fone I told her that I am kinda questioning being her friend. And she asked why.

The reason why my friends is, because everytime I do, as soon as her and her boyfriend get back together I get ditched. Its like hey Kym... Kym who? It has gotten rather old.

Well after I told her that she started bitch and whinning about how she thought I would understand. Ya, whatever save that shit for another dumb friend. I have heard it too many times.

This bothers me so bad. Its like how self absorbed can you be?!?

Oh well.

Ya I have bronchitis.

But oddly enough some black chick actually sat next to Ryan. Ya Hard to believe! Well You know Ryan so funny, and damn talkative. We found out alot about this chick and she worked at the mall and was stranded without a ride. I offered to take her home. She accepted.

Anyway I asked this gurl to come to church with me. I gave her my number and I hope she calls. It felt really good. She seemed to be in need of direction and great ppl. So I thought our church would be perfect.

Maybe this character has is own issues. But um Dude dont' take your lame ass life out on me. Well that is how I felt, I didn't say that.  

But in church saturday we were looking in Romans 13, and while Mr. Corey went on about his *Hunting* trip (who cares), I went back and re-read chapter 12, and in there was a few versus that were so great. 

Do not take revenge, my friends, but leave room for God's wrath, for it is written: "It is mine to avenge: I will repay" says the Lord. On the contrary:

           "If you enemy is hungry, feed him; if he is thristy, give him something to drink. In doing this you will heap burning coals on his head."

Do not be overcome by evil, but overcome evil with good.
                                   -Romans 12:19-21

When I read that, it made so much sense. I don't know how you might take it, but I look at like the old saying... Kill em' with kindess. If you give your enemy water when the are thirsty in some testaments it says that he will fill guilty for his wrong doing upon you. So Like I said... I'ma be killing that kid with Kindness! Oh Ya.
